    "comment": "Rationale: Fig4. vamp2+vamp7+ap3 co-localize in mouse primary neocortical neurons. Antibody against delta subunit of the AP-3 adaptor complex (SA4).\n\nNote: the AP-3 complex location is used as a marker of the endosomal compartment. The study details the co-localization of synaptic vesicle proteins and AP-3 to show that the endosomal compartment is in fact present in the presynapse.. Experimental description: \"Synaptic vesicle and lysosomal AP-3 cargoes colocalization in mouse primary neocortical neurons...\"",
